---
export const prerender = true;
---
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Persona: The Educator | Admin</title>
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" />
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: Inter, system-ui, sans-serif; min-height: 100vh; background: #030712; color: #f9fafb; }
    .header { background: #111827; border-bottom: 1px solid #1f2937; padding: 16px 24px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
    .logo { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fbbf24, #d97706); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
    .back-link { color: #9ca3af; text-decoration: none; font-size: 13px; padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid #374151; }
    .back-link:hover { color: #fbbf24; border-color: #fbbf24; }
    .container { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 32px 24px; }
    .hero { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 32px; padding: 24px; background: #111827; border-radius: 16px; border: 1px solid #1f2937; border-top: 3px solid #ec4899; }
    .hero-icon { font-size: 56px; }
    .hero-name { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; }
    .hero-role { font-size: 13px; color: #ec4899; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
    .section { background: #111827; border: 1px solid #1f2937; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .section-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #fbbf24; margin-bottom: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
    .section p, .section li { font-size: 14px; color: #d1d5db; line-height: 1.7; }
    .section ul { padding-left: 20px; }
    .section li { margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .tag { display: inline-block; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 100px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; background: #500724; color: #f9a8d4; margin: 2px 4px 2px 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <div class="logo">⚙️ xConvert24 Admin</div>
    <a href="/admin/personas" class="back-link">← All Personas</a>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero">
      <div class="hero-icon">📚</div>
      <div>
        <div class="hero-name">The Educator</div>
        <div class="hero-role">Teaching Professional</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">📋 Bio</div>
      <p>The Educator is a teacher, tutor, or instructor who uses xConvert24 as a teaching aid. They demonstrate unit conversions in class, assign students to practice with the tools, and reference the blog posts for educational content. They value accuracy, the formula display, and the visual thermometer/gauge elements.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">🎯 Goals</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Demonstrate conversions visually during lessons</li>
        <li>Assign students to practice specific conversions</li>
        <li>Reference blog posts as supplementary reading material</li>
        <li>Use the formula display to explain the math behind conversions</li>
        <li>Share specific converter links with students</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">😤 Pain Points</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Needs larger font sizes for projector display</li>
        <li>Wants to hide certain UI elements (coins, bookmarks) for cleaner classroom view</li>
        <li>Blog posts sometimes too advanced for younger students</li>
        <li>No "classroom mode" or distraction-free view</li>
        <li>Can't easily create a curated set of converters for a lesson plan</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">🧭 Typical Journey</div>
      <p>Prepares lesson plan → bookmarks 3–4 relevant converters → projects xConvert24 on classroom screen → demonstrates conversions → shares links with students via LMS → students practice independently and earn coins.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">📊 Key Metrics</div>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Visit frequency:</strong> 2–3 times per week (during term)</li>
        <li><strong>Session duration:</strong> 10–30 minutes (during class)</li>
        <li><strong>Primary pages:</strong> /convert/temperature, /convert/length, /convert/weight, blog</li>
        <li><strong>Referral impact:</strong> Each educator drives 10–30 student users</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">🏷️ Tags</div>
      <span class="tag">Classroom Use</span>
      <span class="tag">Visual Learner</span>
      <span class="tag">Multiplier Effect</span>
      <span class="tag">Formula-focused</span>
      <span class="tag">Blog Reader</span>
      <span class="tag">Seasonal</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
